it.cnr.isti.wnlab.indoornavigation.filters.particlefilter

Class IndoorParticleFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.cnr.isti.wnlab.indoornavigation.filters.particlefilter.ParticleFilter<PositionParticle>
      • it.cnr.isti.wnlab.indoornavigation.filters.particlefilter.IndoorParticleFilter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PositionFilter2D, StateEstimationFilter

    public class IndoorParticleFilter
extends ParticleFilter<PositionParticle>
implements PositionFilter2D
    This is a concrete class for Particle Filters for Indoor 2D Localization. Actually this is just an empty (enriched) shell: the policies for updating, filtering, regenerating and picking the position as a result must be injected.
